ite-16px\">最先端の技術に関われる</div>\n        <div class=\"text-4 inter-bold-white-10px\">レンタルサービスを通じて、新しいモノや技術の発展に貢献することができる</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kw-item-1\">\n        <div class=\"text-14 text-15 inter-bold-white-16px\">信頼の三井住友ファイナンス<br><br>&amp;リースグループ</div>\n        <div class=\"sp-about-modal-open-3\" data-modal=\"modal3\">\n          <div class=\"sp-text-left-3 text-4 inter-bold-white-10px\">詳細をみる ↓</div>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"about-sp-mordal-3\" class=\"about-sp-mordal-3\">\n          <img src=\"images/about/sp-modal3.png\" alt=\"\">\n          <br>\n          <button class=\"about-sp-mordal-close-3\">閉じる</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"smp-about-us\">\n      <div class=\"smp-lower-section-title\">\n        <div class=\"overlap-group-3 overlap-group-5\">\n          <img class=\"ellipse-1\" src=\"images/about/ellipse-1-4.svg\" alt=\"Ellipse 1\">\n          <div class=\"smfl notosanscjkjp-bold-blue-whale-24px\">会社情報</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <a href=\"https://www.smfl-r.co.jp/company/profile/\" class=\"button-2\">\n        <div class=\"text-44 valign-text-bottom\">会社情報はこちら</div>\n        <img class=\"icon-1\" src=\"images/top/icon-4.svg\" alt=\"icon\">\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"smp-about-us-1 smp-about-us-2\">\n      <div class=\"smp-lower-section-title\">\n        <div class=\"overlap-group-4 overlap-group-5\">\n          <img class=\"ellipse-1\" src=\"images/about/ellipse-1-3.svg\" alt=\"Ellipse 1\" />\n          <div class=\"smfl notosanscjkjp-bold-blue-whale-24px\">経営理念</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <img src=\"images/about/Frame.jpg\" class=\"frame\">\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div id=\"footer-sp\"></div> -->\n    <footer class=\"mobile-footer\">\n      <img class=\"logo\" src=\"images/footer/logo-1.svg\" alt=\"logo\">\n      <div class=\"copyright\" style=\"width: 100vw;    margin-left: calc((100% - 100vw) / 2);\n      margin-right: calc((100% - 100vw